food Cc Hi eric I just wanted to write and ask what type of foods you like to eat Especially breakfast foods I dont normally keep food in the house and the food I do have is ancient andor not that great Ask Adnan so I wanted to know what you like so I can go grocery shopping and actually cook this weekend Are you a simple guy or are you a bit complex I only have cereal which is what I eat daily But Im sure you have different tastes Adnan likes to have his coffee w a pastry on weekdays and banana pancakes w eggs fruit and bacon on weekends so I have that taken care of but I need to know what you like Another thing We dont want you to worry about spending money on food Youll be well taken care of We wont let you go hungry Anyways hope your excited Talk to you later Maylynn
